<F P=100> REGIONAL ECONOMIC AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Shanghai's 1993 Statistical Communique </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Shanghai's 1993 Statistical Communique </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW0703061194 Shanghai JIEFANG RIBAO in Chinese 15 Feb 94 p 3 </F>
